metadata.name: The Weaver
metadata.description:
The weaver, the creator. The source, the energy. This is the one who weaves Rose. He is the source of energy from which the strands of Rose's material evolves. The weaver is the source of energy and light. 

Rose is made of the same stuff as the stars- the sun. Rose is built from light. "Never stop shining, dear Rose", The Weaver whispers. Her strands are infinitely beautiful. if only she knew the source. 





This is a digitized original 1/1 hand painted piece on a 30x36inches canvas. To be shipped to the collector of this NFT.
